# :TYPE: 45060c5b-2c11-4d98-bbfb-a7b75d3e4dfb
# :ID: `(org-id-new)`

* Introduction

Context that gives meaning to the objective. Plan of the document: objective,
candidate, verification, discussion, and conclusion.
   
* Objective 

A formal description of the objective /i.e./ with a verification
algorithm that allows to decide if the objective is satisfied or not by a given
candidate.
   
* Candidate

The candidate that should satisfy the objective and how it has been built.
    
* Verification

A proof that the candidate satisfies the objective.
   
* Discussion

A discussion of all the above.
   
* Conclusion

A summary of what has been done and future perspectives.
